subject: Basketball (College)
NCAA Basketball Championships (Women)
lead_paragraph: About 2,300 fans saw Duke’s second-round N.C.A.A. tournament win at 9,314-seat Cameron Indoor Stadium. It drew 5,318 and 6,023 to comparable games in 2000 and 2001.
